Package: PhyloTraitDynamics
Title: Companion Code for Phylogenetic Trait Dynamics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Gilles", family = "Didier", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gilles.didier@free.fr")
Author: Gilles Didier
Maintainer: Gilles Didier <gilles.didier@free.fr>
Description: Conservative companion package for reproducing numerical results and figures for an article on birth-death processes, MRCA ages, and Brownian empirical moments on phylogenies. The package exposes a small public API with package-local implementations.
